.SH DATA MODEL
Each application record includes: \- Company \- Role \- Application
status \- Priority (1\(en3) \- Application date \- Source \- Optional
link and location \- Last action (single\-line event) \- Notes (short
contextual text)
.PP
The authoritative definitions for allowed values and formats are
specified in \f[B]CONVENTIONS.md\f[R].
